## 4. Project Setup

### Prerequisites

- Node.js v18.17 or later — [nodejs.org](https://nodejs.org)
- VS Code (recommended)
- Terminal (built into VS Code)

### Create the Project

```bash
npx create-next-app@latest kidlat-civiclabs-website
```

**Recommended setup prompt answers:**

```
✔ TypeScript?          → No
✔ ESLint?              → Yes
✔ Tailwind CSS?        → Yes
✔ src/ directory?      → Yes
✔ App Router?          → Yes
✔ Customize alias?     → No
```

### Install Dependencies

```bash
cd kidlat-civiclabs-website

# Email
npm install resend react-email

# Forms & Validation
npm install react-hook-form zod

# Rate Limiting
npm install @upstash/ratelimit @upstash/redis
