### Core Web Vitals Checklist

- Use `next/image` for all images — auto-compress, lazy load, serve WebP
- Use `next/font` for Gibson/Systemia/Code Pro — eliminates layout shift
- Minimize third-party scripts — each one hurts load time
- Target **Lighthouse 90+** — audit at [pagespeed.web.dev](https://pagespeed.web.dev)

