## 10. Deployment

### Deploy to Vercel

**Recommended: GitHub Integration**

1. Push project to a GitHub repository
2. Go to [vercel.com](https://vercel.com) → Import Project → Select repo
3. Vercel auto-deploys on every push to `main`
4. Add a custom domain: `kidlatciviclabs.org`

### Environment Variables on Vercel

`Settings → Environment Variables → Add`:

```
RESEND_API_KEY
UPSTASH_REDIS_REST_URL
UPSTASH_REDIS_REST_TOKEN
NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL     → https://kidlatciviclabs.org
```

### Post-Deploy Checklist

- [ ] Submit `https://kidlatciviclabs.org/sitemap.xml` to Google Search Console
- [ ] Verify `kidlatciviclabs.org` domain in Resend dashboard
- [ ] Add SPF, DKIM, DMARC DNS records at registrar
- [ ] Run Lighthouse audit — target 90+ score
- [ ] Test contact form end-to-end (check `official@kidlatciviclabs.org`)
- [ ] Set up Google Analytics 4
- [ ] Enable 2FA on Vercel account and domain registrar

